grinding.notes: Grinding is the only practical method

grinding.notes: Diamond wheels essential for this material

materials.name: Chilled Cast Iron (Chill Cast)

materials.notes: Dual-structure iron: hard white iron surface from chill, tough gray iron core.

materials.name: Indefinite Chill Iron (ICDP Roll)
materials.notes: ICDP - Indefinite Chill Double Pour. Excellent thermal fatigue for mill rolls.
